        <h2 id="utilities-inventory">1c. Utilities & Helper Classes Inventory (16 Utilities)</h2>
        
        <div class="alert alert-info">
            <h4>🔧 System Utility Classes & Support Infrastructure</h4>
            <p>Comserv contains <strong>16 utility modules</strong> providing cross-cutting functionality for authentication, configuration, backup, infrastructure, and system operations. These utilities are used by multiple controllers to share common logic and prevent code duplication.</p>
        </div>

        <table class="features-table" style="width: 100%; margin: 20px 0;">
